18 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
19 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 803 of Title 17, unless there is
20 created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
21 A. Not later than ninety (90) days after the effective date of
22 this act, the Corporation Commission shall start the process to
23 engage an outside consulting firm to conduct a technical and legal
24 feasibility study on nuclear energy generation in this state. This
